Package camzup.kotlin

Class KtQuat

java.lang.Object
camzup.core.Quaternion
camzup.kotlin.KtQuat
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Quaternion>
public class KtQuat
extends Quaternion
Provides Kotlin operator overloading support for quaternions.
